																				<h3>About</h3>
																					

										
																																																					

										
																		   									   										<div class="tab_column_left">
											<div class="secondary_content_container">
																							 <p>BMC offers IT management solutions that help customers master the complexity of IT. From mainframe to mobile, BMC delivers the automation, integration, and sophistication that enable the business and IT to perform like never before.</p>
<p><strong>Mission</strong><br />
Provide innovative IT management solutions that improve how digital services are delivered and consumed.</p>
<p><strong>Commitment to Customer Success</strong><br />
We serve more than 10,000 customers in more than 120 countries including: 100% of the Forbes Global 100, 86% of the Forbes Global 500, 92% of the Fortune 100 and 82% of the Fortune 500 companies.</p>
<p>Check out these customer successes:</p>
<div class="careers_tab_hold"><a href="/videos/customer-success/adobe.html"><img src="http://media.cms.bmc.com/images/careers-adobe-vdo.png" alt="" /></a>
<p class="careers_tab_hold_txt"><a href="/videos/customer-success/adobe.html"><strong>Adobe IT transforms business with BMC</strong> - Cloud/SaaS</a><br />
Just a few years ago, Adobe sold packaged software to creative professionals &mdash; and they led the industry in doing so. Today, their IT department is credited with helping Adobe transform their entire business model, from selling boxes of software to offering online subscription services, turning Adobe into the global leader in digital marketing and digital media solutions</p>
<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
<div class="careers_tab_hold"><a href="/videos/customer-success/207873381.html"><img src="http://media.cms.bmc.com/images/careers-chiprewards-vdo.png" alt="" /></a>
<p class="careers_tab_hold_txt"><a href="/videos/customer-success/207873381.html"><strong>ChipRewards Drives Big Data Analytics with BMC</strong> - WLA</a><br />
ChipRewards uses Control-M Workload Automation for batch processing and cloud resourcing for the big data analytics that is central to their business.</p>
<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>
