<p class="careers_tab_hold_txt"><a href="/videos/customer-success/thai-airways-remedy-video.html"><strong>Thai Airways Streamlines IT Operations with BMC</strong> - ITSM</a><br />
BMC's Remedy platform underpins the robust and efficient Thai Airways information systems.</p>
